  "body": "### Description\r\nAs a node operator, I want to enable support for HTTP/2 over TLS so that clients can use HTTP2/multiplexing  to reduce the number of connections to the server and improve performance.\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n* When TLS is enabled server supports both HTTP/1.1 and HTTP/2 (h2) connections\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\nSimple testing with okhttpclient shows a significant reduction in request time for multiple requests when server enabled for HTTP/2 support. \r\n\r\none line addition in JsonRpcHttpService.java\r\n\r\nhttpServerOptions.setUseAlpn(true)\r\n\r\n",
